===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[四]] || [[ヶ]] || [[月]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
[[四]] (よん, ''yon'') "four" + [[ヶ]] ([[箇]], か, ''ka''), the counter for months + [[月]] (げつ, ''getsu'') "month"

===Noun===
'''四ヶ月''' ([[よんかげつ]], ''yonkagetsu'')

# [[四箇月]]: four months (duration)

